snippet.description:
BINI | ‘Sweet Tooth’ Official Music Video

#BINI :  “Sweet Tooth” is a shimmering, slow-burn pop song with a deceptively soft exterior. Equal parts tender and addictive, the song turns desire into a metaphor for sugar, with lines that confess a compulsive need for more. Just like candy, there can be too much of a good thing, especially when you know it’s not good for you. But unlike this song, this guilty-free pleasure will keep you listening over and over again 

#BINI_SweetTooth and the #BINI_FLAMES album is now on all platforms: https://orcd.co/bini_flames

snippet.title: Moana | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
#Moana, arriving only in theaters July 10, 2026 🌊 Watch the new teaser now!

In Disney’s live-action adaptation of the beloved Oscar®-nominated animated adventure, Moana (Catherine Lagaʻaia) answers the Ocean’s call and, for the first time, voyages beyond the reef of her island of Motunui with the infamous demigod Maui (Dwayne Johnson) on an unforgettable journey to restore prosperity to her people. The film is directed by Emmy® and Tony Award® winner Thomas Kail (“Hamilton”); produced by Dwayne Johnson, Dany Garcia, Beau Flynn, Hiram Garcia and Lin-Manuel Miranda; and executive produced by Thomas Kail, Scott Sheldon, Charles Newirth and Auliʻi Cravalho, who voiced Moana in the animated features “Moana” and “Moana 2.” Audiences can experience the brilliant cinematic sights, sounds and songs of “Moana” in U.S. theaters on July 10, 2026.

#PaskongPinoy2026 #TagalogChristmasSongs #FilipinoHolidayMusic #ChristmasMedley2026 #PinoyChristmas
 
Welcome to Paskong Serenata, where the glow of Filipino Christmas shines through timeless carols and heartfelt melodies. Each track is a tribute to our cherished holiday spirit — joy, family, faith, and the warmth of home.

🎧 Tracklist Highlights:
– Modern renditions of beloved Tagalog Christmas songs
– Soft instrumental and vocal reworks made with love
– Studio-quality sound blending nostalgia and new energy

🎨 Production:
All music and visuals are originally created in-house — a fusion of Filipino creativity and modern tools (Veo3, ChatGPT, After Effects, CapCut). Every note and light flicker is designed to bring the parol’s glow to life.

🙏 From our studio to your home: thank you for listening, sharing, and keeping the spirit of Pasko alive.
Maligayang Pasko at Manigong Bagong Taon! 🎅💫💚
